    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Reference is made to your telephonic conversation with the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Director on Wednesday of last week, at which time the Director advised",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "that Los Angeles papers carried under a Washington date line an article",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "indicating the Soviet espionage agents in the United States are under",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "instruction to solve the flying discs. Such instructions were believed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "to be based on the assumption that the flying discs were a secret weapon",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "of the Army or Navy. The article attributed the source of its information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "to a Federal investigative agency.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Pursuant to your instructions, liaison representatives have contacted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "the Headquarters of Military Intelligence, the Headquarters of the Air Forces",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Intelligence, Office of Naval Intelligence and CIG. All agencies denied any",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "knowledge of the flying discs, as well as any knowledge of the basis for this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
